{"tid":2180473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831標語被清 但係我地唔會忘記","createTime":"2020-08-30T01:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T19:03:26.000Z","uid":28891,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4ecc1fba0e82c40601ad28e66fcf01f7716111","tid":2180473,"uid":28891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"凌晨三時許有數名警員到場把貼在觀塘港鐵站往裕民坊出口有關831事件的大型標語清理，該標語由午夜就已經張貼於上址，惟凌晨時分該標語被五名疑似警員的便裝男子清除。同時，有警員截停搜查在場記者身分證，並命令記者離開現場，清理後標語仍清晰可見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWwjsyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWwjsyd.jpg&h=c26313c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114718626608158/posts/338218160924869/?extid=i7pWrunOlJuZ7aSL&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114718626608158%2Fposts%2F338218160924869%2F%3Fextid%3Di7pWrunOlJuZ7aSL%26d%3Dn&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=be63694a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114718626608158/posts/338218160924869/?extid=i7pWrunOlJuZ7aSL&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n清完都仲睇到 證明有啲野發生左就發生左 唔會話你唔講就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fdbcb4b266fbb7c4de3a8e55d88cff697b4567","tid":2180473,"uid":28891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"831打死人"},{"pid":"116c92679d768307f33554cb594bc6496d56cc4f","tid":2180473,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a835b09d17449d56183ad8164b4504a1b4c1f0ac","tid":2180473,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89fdbcb4b266fbb7c4de3a8e55d88cff697b4567","tid":2180473,"uid":28891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"831打死人"},"citedBy":0,"r